messages.message:
Hi team,

I'm on as a community user. I'm noticing that the + button for 'projects' sometimes disappears, despite me having credits. Sometimes, the + button appears, but I can't consistently reproduce when it appears/disappears. This is on https://aihub-sandbox.internal.instabase.com/hub. I am still able to create projects through the build app.
It looks like a bug that was introduced a while ago when we changed activeOrgContext to always have an active organization. I'll get a fix in ASAP. It should probably be backported
